m%2FHillaryClinton%2Fstatus%2F1765383507528884462%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ad%2C%20Biden%20highlights%20his%20accomplishments%20and%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%20we're%20rebuilding%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20jibes%20at%20his%20top%20opponent%2C%20calling%20Trump%20out%20for%20failing%20to%20pass%20an%20infrastructure%20law%20as%20president%2C%20which%20Biden%20later%20successfully%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20believes%20the%20job%20of%20the%20president%20is%20to%20take%20care%20of%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%94%20I%20believe%20the%20job%20of%20the%20American%20president%20is%20to%20fight%20for%20you%2C%20the%20american%20people%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20what%20I'm%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20and%20I%20approve%20this%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20we%20do%20one%20more%20take%3F%26quot%3B%20a%20voice%20asks%20toward%20the%20end%20before%20the%20camera%20refocuses%20on%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I'm%20very%20young%2C%20energetic%2C%20and%20handsome%E2%80%94%20what%20the%20hell%20am%20I%20doing%20this%20for%3F%26quot%3B%20quips%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2060-second%20ad%20will%20run%20for%20six%20weeks%20on%20various%20networks%2C%20including%20ESPN%2C%20TNT%2C%20Comedy%20Central%2C%20and%20FX%2C%20targeting%20key%20swing%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20used%20self-effacing%20humor%20similarly%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-biden-age-reference-state-of-the-union-speech-2024-2024-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAt%252081%252C%2520Biden%2520is%2520the%2Cpresident%2520in%2520the%2520nation%2527s%2520history.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20during%20his%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20remarks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20it%20may%20not%20look%20like%20it%2C%20but%20I've%20been%20around%20a%2