y%20filmed%20an%20MLA's%20son%20in%20a%20compromising%20situation%20and%20attempted%20to%20blackmail%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%9A%A0%EF%B8%8FScam%20Alert%E2%9A%A0%EF%B8%8F%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20got%20a%20call%20about%20an%20hour%20ago%20from%20an%20unknown%20number.%20I%20unusually%20do%20not%20respond%20to%20unknown%20numbers%20but%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20made%20me%20answer%20this%20call.%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20the%20other%20end%20was%20a%20guy%20who%20said%20he%20is%20a%20cop%20and%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20knew%20where%20my%20daughter%20K%20is.%20He%20said%20K%20gave...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Kaveri%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40ikaveri)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fikaveri%2Fstatus%2F1767078463532614011%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20soon%20realised%20that%20it%20was%20a%20scam%20and%20activated%20call%20recording%20and%20requested%20to%20speak%20with%20her%20daughter.%20%26quot%3BThe%20man%20sounded%20rough%20and%20rude%20throughout%20the%20call.%20To%20my%20horror%2C%20a%20recording%20was%20played%20to%20me%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Emumma%20mujhe%20bacha%20lo%2C%20mumma%20mujhe%20bacha%20lo%3C%2Fem%3E..%26quot%3B%20(Mom%2C%20save%20me%2C%20save%20me)%20The%20voice%20sounded%20exactly%20like%20my%20daughters%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20way%20she%20would%20have%20spoken%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mother%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaveri%20said%20the%20fake%20cop%20demanded%20money%20in%20exchange%20for%20her%20daughter%20and%20would%20drop%20the%20case%20altogether.%20%26quot%3BI%20asked%20him%20to%20let%20me%20speak%20to%20my%20daughter%20properly.%20He%20got%20all%20angry%20and%20rude.%20We%20are%20taking%20her%20away%20then%2C%20he%20said.%20Ok%2C%20take%20her%20away%20then%2C%20I%20told%20him.%20And%20I%20laughed.%20He%20cut%20the%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaveri%20said%20it%20was%20all%20a%20scheme%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20replicate%20her%20daughter's%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaveri's%20post%20soon%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20social%20media%20users%20and%20numerous%20users%20shared%20similar%20encounters%20in%20the%20comment%20section.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20shared%2C%20%26quot%3BOmg%20this%20happened%20to%20a%20friend%20back%20in%20Assam.%20Got%20a%20call%20late%20night%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bcop%26quot%3B%20who%20asked%20if%20he%20has%20P's%20dad%2C%20P%20who%20studies%20here%20and%20lives%20at%20this%20address%20in%20PG%20(across%20the%20country).%20And%20then%20told%20him%20she's%20been%20arrested%20for%20possession%20of%20drugs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20similar%20thing%20happened%20with%20my%20mum.%20Though%20my%20brother%20lives%20out%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20tone%20in%20which%20the%20self-proclaimed%20ASI%20threatened%20my%20mother%20about%20his%20whereabouts%2C%20she%20was%20really%20scared.%20It%20was%20a%20WhatsApp%20call%20and%20the%20DP%20had%20a%20man%20wearing%20a%20police%20uniform%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20user%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20user%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BTo%20prevent%20this%20kind%20of%20scam%2C%20some%20people%20started%20using%20passwords%20that%20only%20their%20family%20members%20would%20know%2C%20the%20person%20with%20AI%20voice%20won't%20know%20this%2C%20I%20removed%20my%20videos%2C%20and%20audio%20from%20the%20internet%20for%20the%20same%20reason.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUff%20this%20is%20very%20scary.%20I'm%20assuming%20they%20also%20know%20when%20your%20daughter%20is%20not%20actually%20with%20you.%20How%20scary%20is%20that!%20They%20know%20your%20number%2C%20your%20name%2C%20your%20daughter's%20name%2C%20and%20some%20possible%20info%20about%20her%20whereabouts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20fourth%20user%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20concerning%20part%20is%20your%20daughter's%20recorded%20voice.%20Needless%20to%20say%20the%20scammer%20used%20AI%20tools%20but%20getting%20access%20to%20voice%20samples%20is%20something%20that%20could%20give%20sleepless%20nights%20to%20every%20parent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20fifth%20user%20commented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710153360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fcrtv8aro_call-generic_625x300_11_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-ai-scam-a-fake-cop-spoke-to-woman-said-her-daughter-was-arrested-5217847%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kaveri%20said%20it%20was%20all%20a%20scheme%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20replicate%20her%20daughter's%20voice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-ai-scam-a-fake-cop-spoke-to-woman-said-her-daughter-was-arrested-5217847%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-ai-scam-a-fake-cop-spoke-to-woman-said-her-daughter-was-arrested-5217847%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-ai-scam-a-fake-cop-spoke-to-woman-said-her-daughter-was-arrested-5217847%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20Court%20Setback%20For%20Bengal%2C%20Probe%20Against%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20Stays%20With%20CBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20dismissed%20its%20challenge%20to%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20order%20that%20transferred%20to%20the%20CBI%20the%20investigation%20into%20an%20attack%20on%20a%20team%20of%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20officials%20in%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali.%20A%20team%20of%20ED%20officials%20had%20come%20under%20a%20mob%20attack%20on%20January%205%20when%20they%20went%20to%20the%20island%20to%20question%20local%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20also%20questioned%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20why%20it%20took%2050%20days%20to%20arrest%20Shahjahan.%20The%20now-expelled%20Trinamool%20leader%20is%20in%20the%20CBI's%20custody.%20Besides%20the%20case%20relating%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20ED%20team%2C%20the%20strongman%20and%20his%20aides%20face%20allegations%20of%20land%20grab%2C%20extortion%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20last%20week%20asked%20Bengal%20police%20to%20hand%20over%20Shahjahan's%20custody%20to%20the%20central%20agency.%20It%20had%20also%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20state%20police.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20expunged%20the%20high%20court's%20observations%20on%20Bengal%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20query%20on%20why%20it%20took%2050%20days%20to%20arrest%20the%20strongman%2C%20Bengal%20police%20said%20a%20high%20court%20order%20had%20paused%20the%20investigation.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20stay%20on%20investigation.%20We%20went%20back%20to%20court%2C%20asking%20for%20a%20clarification.%20It%20was%20clarified.%20Within%20one%20day%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20Senior%20Advocate%20Jaideep%20Gupta%2C%20appearing%20for%20Bengal%20government%2C%20told%20the%20court.%C2%A0%26quot%3BTo%20say%20that%20the%20state%20police%20is%20delaying%20the%20investigation...these%20kinds%20of%20allegations%20are%20very%20damaging%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposing%20the%20Bengal%20government%2C%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%20referred%20to%20the%20January%205%20incident.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIn%20a%20case%20involving%20a%20ration%20scam%20running%20into%20crores%20of%20rupees%2C%20ED%20officials%20went%20to%20(the)%20house%20of%20this%20main%20accused.%20The%20door%20was%20not%20open%20and%20they%20were%20beaten%20up.%20They%20tried%20to%20water%20down%20the%20case%2C%20insofar%20as%20the%20assault%20of%20the%20ED%20officer%20is%20concerned.%20They%20filed%20some%20other%20case.%20That's%20why%20the%20investigation%20was%20stayed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0The%20Centre's%20counsel%20said%20Bengal%20police%20made%20%26quot%3Bno%20serious%20effort%26quot%3B%20to%20enter%20Shahjahan's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20several%20cases%20of%20harassment%20against%20him.%20He%20has%20been%20patronised%20by%20local%20police%20and%20politicians.%20(For)%2057%20days%2C%20he%20is%20not%20available.%20Then%20overnight%20he%20appears%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Raju%20also%20contested%20the%20state%20government's%20argument%20that%20a%20pause%20in%20the%20investigation%20stopped%20state%20police%20from%20arresting%20Shahjahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20also%20appearing%20for%20Bengal%20government%2C%20flagged%20the%20high%20court's%20remarks%20on%20state%20police.%20When%20Mr%20Raju%20said%20these%20observations%20may%20be%20deleted%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20those%20observations%20are%20deleted%2C%20then%20what%20are%20the%20grounds%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20observations%20against%20the%20police%20and%20the%20State%20government%20are%20deemed%20to%20be%20expunged%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20by%20residents%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20an%20island%20in%20Bengal's%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20have%20raised%20a%20political%20storm%20in%20the%20state.%20Shahjahan%2C%20who%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20these%20allegations%2C%20was%20arrested%20last%20month%20after%20he%20was%20on%20the%20run%20for%20over%2050%20days.%20What%20followed%20was%20a%20dramatic%20tug%20of%20war%20between%20central%20agencies%20and%20state%20police%20for%20the%20strongman's%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20occasion%2C%20the%20state%20cops%20refused%20to%20hand%20him%20over%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20state%20government's%20challenge%20to%20the%20high%20court%20in%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20high%20court%2C%20however%2C%20held%20that%20its%20order%20had%20not%20been%20paused%20and%20directed%20Bengal%20police%20to%20hand%20over%20Shahjahan%20to%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710153300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fe14mic4o_sheikh-shahjahan_625x300_29_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-sandeshkhali-case-sheikh-shahjahan-top-court-setback-for-bengal-probe-against-sheikh-shahjahan-stays-with-cbi-5217795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20dismissed%20its%20challenge%20to%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20order%20that%20transferred%20to%20the%20CBI%20the%20investigation%20into%20an%20attack%20on%20a%20team%20of%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20officials%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-sandeshkhali-case-sheikh-shahjahan-top-court-setback-for-bengal-probe-against-sheikh-shahjahan-stays-with-cbi-5217795%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-sandeshkhali-case-sheikh-shahjahan-top-court-setback-for-bengal-probe-against-sheikh-shahjahan-stays-with-cbi-5217795%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-sandeshkhali-case-sheikh-shahjahan-top-court-setback-for-bengal-probe-against-sheikh-shahjahan-stays-with-cbi-5217795%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20passes%20law%20granting%20Communist%20Party%20more%20control%20over%20cabinet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710153148000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiim