%20action%20against%20the%20accused%20was%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20did%2C%20however%2C%20complain%20about%20children%20today%20%26quot%3Bgrappling%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20watching%20pornography%2C%20declaring%20it%20could%20have%20negative%20consequences%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20declaring%20the%20accused%20to%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bafflicted%20with%20this%20(watching%20pornography)%20addiction%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20advised%20counselling%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%20and%20happy%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20central%20government%20sent%20notices%20to%20social%20media%20platforms%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20Telegram%2C%20warning%20they%20would%20lose%20legal%20immunity%20unless%20they%20act%20on%20this%20issue%20urgently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platforms%20were%20asked%20to%20permanently%20remove%2C%20or%20disable%20access%20to%2C%20child%20pornography%20content.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fact-on-child-pornography-or-lose-legal-immunity-centre-to-tech-giants-4457056%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAct%20Against%20Child%20Porn%2C%20Or%20Lose%20Legal%20Immunity%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre%20To%20Tech%20Giants%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centre's%20action%20followed%20reports%20that%20another%20social%20media%20platform%20-%20Instagram%20-%20is%20home%20to%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20such%20content%20being%20created%20and%20shared.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finstagrams-algorithms-connect-vast-paedophile-network-seeking-child-pornography-report-4103916%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%20report%20said%C2%A0Instagram's%20algorithms%20linked%20and%20promoted%20this%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20people%20seeking%20illegal%20sexual%20content%20and%