nd%20Gurugram%20on%20NH-48.%20The%20expressway%20will%20cut%20the%20travel%20time%20by%20at%20least%2020%20minutes%20for%2090%2C000%20commuters%20who%20take%20this%20route%20every%20day.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20construction%20of%20Dwarka%20Expressway%2C%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20people%20used%20to%20avoid%20coming%20here%20after%20dusk.%20Even%20taxi%20drivers%20used%20to%20refuse%20and%20the%20entire%20area%20was%20considered%20unsafe.%20Today%2C%20many%20big%20companies%20are%20setting%20up%20their%20projects%20here.%20This%20area%20is%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20developing%20areas%20of%20NCR%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20expressway%20in%20India%20built%20on%20single%20pillars%20and%20has%20several%20underpasses%20and%20service%20roads%20along%20its%2018-km%20stretch.%20The%20eight-lane%20expressway%20provides%20direct%20connectivity%20to%20the%20Delhi%20International%20Airport%20and%20Gurugram%20Bypass.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20expressway%20was%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20nearly%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%2C%20out%20of%C2%A0which%20the%20Haryana%20segment%20was%20built%20at%20Rs%204%2C100%20crore.%20This%20includes%20a%2010.2-km%20stretch%20linking%20the%20Delhi-Haryana%20Border%20with%20Basai%20Rail-over-Bridge%20(ROB)%20and%20an%208.7-km%20stretch%20between%20Basai%20ROB%20and%20Kherki%20Daula.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20is%20among%20the%20highway%20projects%20worth%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore%20that%20PM%20Modi%20inaugurated%20and%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stones%20for.%20The%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20Bharatmala%20Project%2C%20a%20flagship%20infrastructure%20project%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETraffic%20restrictions%20were%20in%20place%20at%20border%20areas%20between%20Delhi%20and%20Gurugram%20in%20view%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20event.%20Delhi%20and%20Gurugram%20Police%20have%20issued%20traffic%20advisories.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOther%20major%20projects%20inaugurated%20today%20include%20a%209.6-km%20six-lane%20Urban%20Extension%20Road-II%20(UER-II)-Package%203%20between%20Nangloi-Najafgarh%20Road%20and%20Sector%2024%20Dwarka%20section%20in%20Delhi.%20Three%20sections%20of%20the%20Lucknow%20Ring%20Road%20and%20the%20Anandapuram-Pendurthi-Anakapalli%20phase%20of%20NH-16%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20were%20also%20inaugurated.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFrom%20the%20event%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20launched%20projects%20worth%20Rs%203%2C400%20crore%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Rs%202%2C750%20crore%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Rs%2020%2C500%20crore%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHighway%20projects%20for%20which%20foundation%20stones%20were%20laid%20today%20include%2014%20sections%20of%20the%20Bengaluru-Kadappa-Vijayawada%20Expressway%20and%20six%20packages%20of%20the%20Belgaum-Hungund-Raichur%20section%20of%20NH-748A%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20foundation%20stones%20of%20different%20sections%20of%20the%20Shamli-Ambala%20Highway%20in%20Haryana%20and%20the%20Amritsar-Bathinda%20corridor%20in%20Punjab%20were%20also%20laid%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710149700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F0f0c9qi_haryana-section-of-dwarka-expressway_625x300_11_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-phase-of-dwarka-expressway-opens-today-to-cut-delhi-gurugram-travel-time-5216531%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20inaugurated%20a%20key%20phase%20of%20the%20landmark%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20that%20would%20ease%20the%20traffic%20on%20the%20Delhi-Gurugram%20route.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-phase-of-dwarka-expressway-opens-today-to-cut-delhi-gurugram-travel-time-5216531%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22