fter%20his%20arrest%20last%20year%2C%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20Kapu%20samaj%20votes%20due%20to%20the%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20factor%2C%20and%20Jagan's%20failure%20at%20achieving%20a%20special%20category%20status%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Ironically%2C%20the%20last%20bit%20was%20the%20same%20weapon%20Jagan%20had%20to%20unseat%20Naidu%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENaidu%20In%20A%20Tight%20Spot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20TDP%20does%20well%2C%20it%20will%20add%20a%20few%20seats%20to%20the%20NDA's%20kitty%20and%20help%20its%20Mission%20400.%20Its%20failure%20to%20do%20so%20could%20lead%20to%20an%20existential%20crisis%20for%20the%20party%20and%20open%20up%20a%20gap-which%2C%20party%20strategists%20hope%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%20able%20to%20fill.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Naidu%2C%20this%20is%20a%20do-or-die%20battle%20and%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20leave%20anything%20to%20chance.%20With%20BJP%20on%20its%20side%2C%20the%20TDP%20hopes%20to%20give%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20the%20formidable%20Jagan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710148200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F07rsj664_bjp-tdp-alliance_640x480_08_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-andhras-tdp-bjp-alliance-stakes-are-higher-for-naidu-5217372%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20BJP%20on%20its%20side%2C%20the%20TDP%20hopes%20to%20give%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20the%20formidable%20Jagan%20Reddy.%20However%2C%20a%20not-so-good%20performance%20can%20lead%20to%20an%20existential%20crisis%20for%20Naidu's%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22c