%20Canadian%20store%20locations%20after%20filing%20for%20bankruptcy%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20The%20Body%20Shop%2C%20in%20an%20official%20release%2C%20announced%20that%20its%20US%20subsidiary%20was%20no%20longer%20operational%2C%20effective%20March%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20added%20that%2033%20of%20its%20105%20stores%20in%20Canada%20will%20begin%20liquidation%20sales%20immediately%20and%20%26quot%3Bonline%20sales%20via%20Canada's%20e-commerce%20store%20will%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20all%20Canadian%20locations%20will%20remain%20open%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%20reported%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20high%20inflation%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20affected%20traditional%20retailers%2C%20particularly%20those%20like%20The%20Body%20Shop%2C%20which%20predominantly%20operated%20out%20of%20malls%20and%20were%20aimed%20at%20the%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK-based%20cosmetics%20company%2C%20founded%20in%201976%20by%20human%20rights%20activist%20and%20environmental%20campaigner%20Anita%20Roddick%2C%20is%20known%20for%20products%20it%20markets%20as%20natural%2C%20sustainable%2C%20ethical%20and%20cruelty-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20companies%20to%20prohibit%20testing%20on%20animals%20for%20many%20of%20its%20products%2C%20according%20to%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%202019%2C%20it%20was%20certified%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BB%20Corp%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20designation%20given%20to%20companies%20that%20meet%20certain%20transparency%20and%20environmental%20conscientiousness%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202023%2C%20it%20had%20expanded%20to%20more%20than%202%2C500%20retail%20locations%20in%20over%2080%20countries%20and%20was%20available%20to%20purchase%20online%20in%20more%20than%2060%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20inception%2C%20The%20Body%20Shop%20has%20changed%20hands%20several%20times.%20It%20was%20purchased%20by%20cosmetics%20giant%20L'Oreal%20in%202006%20for%20more%20than%20a%20billion%20dollars%20and%20later%20sold%20to%20Brazilian%20company%20Natura%20in%202017%20for%20another%20billion%20dollars%2C%20reported%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20brand%20fell%20into%20hard%20times%20and%20has%20been%20ailing%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20early%202023%20report%2C%20Natura%20noted%20that%20The%20Body%20Shop%20was%20%26quot%3B(facing)%20headwinds%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20year-over-year%20decline%20of%2013.5%20per%20cent%20in%202022%2C%20a%20year%20the%20company%20said%20%26quot%3Bwas%20far%20from%20easy%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20brand.%20Its%20direct-to-consumer%20channels%2C%20which%20had%20%26quot%3Bbenefitted%20during%20COVID-19%2C%26quot%3B%20returned%20to%20%26quot%3Bmore%20normalized%20pre-pandemic%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20further%20impacting%20sales%20numbers%2C%20Natura%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20late%20last%20year%2C%20The%20Body%20Shop%20was%20sold%20to%20asset%20management%20group%20Aurelius%20for%20about%20USD%20266%20million%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710145620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Frchha3b_makeup-remover_625x300_10_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcosmetics-firm-the-body-shop-goes-bankrupt-shuts-down-us-canada-stores-5216334%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UK-based%20cosmetics%20company%2C%20The%20Body%20Shop%2C%20shut%20down%20all%20of%20its%20US-based%20operations%20and%20will%20soon%20be%20closing%20dozens%20of%20Canadian%20store%20locations%20after%20filing%20for%20bankruptcy%2C%20CNN%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcosmetics-firm-the-body-shop-goes-bankrupt-shuts-down-us-canada-stores-5216334%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-