egulations-study%2Farticle67936093.ece%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20Indian%20gig%20workers%20has%20revealed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20study%2C%20conducted%20by%20People%E2%80%99s%20Association%20in%20Grassroots%20Action%20and%20Movements%20and%20the%20Indian%20Federation%20of%20App-based%20Transport%20Workers%2C%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgig-workers-suffer-from-lack-of-social-security-regulations-study%2Farticle67936093.ece%5C%22%3Esocial%20disparities%20are%20replicated%20in%20gig%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20only%2016%25%20of%20drivers%20from%20the%20unreserved%20category%20working%20for%20more%20than%2014%20hours%20as%20opposed%20to%2060%25%20of%20drivers%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Tribes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20study%2C%20involving%205%2C302%20cab%20drivers%20and%205%2C028%20delivery%20persons%20across%20eight%20cities%2C%20also%20revealed%20other%20alarming%20trends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFinancial%20struggle%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%2043%25%20of%20participants%20earn%20less%20than%20Rs%20500%20a%20day%2C%20or%20Rs%2015%2C000%20a%20month%20after%20deducting%20all%20costs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENearly%2034%25%20app-based%20delivery%20workers%20earn%20less%20than%20Rs%2010%2C000%20a%20month%20while%2078%25%20work%20over%2010%20hours%20a%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHighlighting%20the%20differences%20among%20workers%20from%20different%20castes%2C%20the%20report%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthese%20income%20disparities%20further%20exacerbate%20the%20already%20existing%20social%20inequalities%20and%20perpetuate%20cycles%20of%20poverty%20and%20distress%20within%20these%20communities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20noted%20that%20drivers%20are%20physically%20exhausted%20and%20exposed%20to%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20road%20traffic%20accidents%20due%20to%20long%20working%20hours.%20This%20is%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9810-minute%20delivery%20at%20the%20doorstep%E2%80%99%20policy%20of%20certain%20e-commerce%20platforms.%20The%20report%20said%20that%2086%25%20of%20delivery%20persons%20found%20such%20policies%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20unacceptable%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20study%20also%20found%20that%20nearly%2072%25%20cab%20drivers%20and%2076%25%20delivery%20workers%20are%20unable%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20with%2068%25%20of%20the%20latter%20reporting%20more%20expenses%20than%20their%20income.%20The%20report%20strongly%20advocates%20for%20better%20compensation%20and%20support%20for%20these%20app-based%20workers%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgig-workers-suffer-from-lack-of-social-security-regulations-study%2Farticle67936093.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EUnfair%20compensation%2C%20no%20time%20off%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%2080%25%20of%20app-based%20cab%20drivers%20and%2073%25%20of%20delivery%20persons%20expressed%20dissatisfaction%20with%20their%20fares%20and%20rates%20respectively.%20Respondents%20believe%20that%20companies%20deduct%20between%2031-40%25%20of%20the%20commission%20rate%20per%20ride%2C%20contrary%20to%20officially%20claimed%20figures%20of%2020%25%2C%20with%2068%25%20finding%20these%20deductions%20arbitrary%2C%20unexplained%2C%20and%20unfair.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20the%20low%20pay%2C%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20workers%20struggled%20to%20take%20time%20off%20with%2041%25%20of%20drivers%20and%2048%25%20of%20delivery%20persons%20being%20unable%20to%20take%20a%20single%20day%20off%20in%20a%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20highlighted%20the%20issue%20of%20ID%20deactivation%20and%20customer%20misbehaviour.%20%E2%80%9CA%20glaring%2083%25%20of%20the%20drivers%20reported%20that%20the%20issue%20of%20ID%20blocking%20affects%20them%20negatively%2C%2047%25%20stated%20that%20this%20issue%20extremely%20affects%20them.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20delivery%20persons%2C%20this%20percentage%20is%20even%20higher%20at%2087%25.%20Customer%20behaviour%20affects%20a%20significant%20majority%20(72%25)%20of%20drivers%20in%20a%20negative%20way%2C%20while%2068%25%20of%20delivery%20persons%20are%20reportedly%20affected%20by%20it%20negatively%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgig-workers-suffer-from-lack-of-social-security-regulations-study%2Farticle67936093.ece%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710140311000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F11165805%2FScreen-Shot-2019-09-11-at-4.57.43-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2F14-hour-work-day-no-time-off-unfair-compensation-a-new-study-on-gig-workers-reveals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20report%20found%20that%20social%20disparities%20are%20replicated%20in%20gig%20work%20with%20only%2016%25%20of%20drivers%20from%20the%20unreserved%20category%20working%20for%20more%20than%2014%20hours%20as%20opposed%20to%2060%25%20of%20drivers%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Tribes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2F14-hour-work-day-no-time-off-unfair-compensation-a-new-study-on-gig-workers-reveals%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SBI%20Plea%20For%20Time%20To%20Submit%20Poll%20Bonds%20Info%20Dismissed%3A%20What%20Top%20Court%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20submissions%20of%20the%20SBI%20sufficiently%20indicate%20that%20the%20information%20is%20readily%20available.%20The%20Application%20filed%20by%20the%20SBI%20seeki