d%20a%20free%20trade%20agreement%20on%20Sunday%20(March%2010)%20in%20which%20the%20bloc%20promises%20investment%20of%20%24100%20billion%20in%20India%20in%20return%20for%20relaxed%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalks%20over%20the%20trade%20deal%20between%20India%20and%20the%20European%20Free-Trade%20Association%20(EFTA)%20%E2%80%93%20comprising%20Switzerland%2C%20Norway%2C%20Iceland%20and%20Liechtenstein%20%E2%80%93%20began%20in%202008%20and%20have%20involved%2021%20rounds%20of%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%24100%20billion%20investment%20into%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy%20will%20take%20place%20over%20a%20time%20period%20of%2015%20years%2C%20during%20which%20the%20creation%20of%20about%20ten%20lakh%20jobs%20will%20be%20facilitated%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Findia-efta-trade-agreement-100-billion-deal-9205865%2F%5C%22%3EUnion%20commerce%20minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20said%20today%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20investment%20will%20come%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-10%2Findia-efta-bloc-sign-free-trade-pact-after-16-years-in-making%5C%22%3Emostly%20from%20the%20private%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bloomberg%20cited%20Goyal%20as%20saying.%20The%20news%20agency%20previously%20reported%20that%20it%20would%20likely%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-07%2Findia-eyes-100-billion-investment-deal-with-switzerland-norway%5C%22%3Etargeted%20at%20manufacturing%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20deal%2C%20EFTA%20countries%20will%20face%20reduced%20tariffs%20for%20processed%20foods%20and%20beverages%20as%20well%20as%20for%20electrical%20machinery.%20Their%20pharmaceutical%20and%20medical%20devices%20industries%20will%20also%20benefit%2C%20Bloomberg%E2%80%99s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added