0of%20government%20data%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20analysis%2C%20we%20considered%2019%20MPs%20based%20on%20the%20profession%20they%20had%20listed%20in%20their%20election%20affidavit.%20These%20professions%20include%20actor%2Factress%2C%20singer-actor%2C%20artist%2C%20sportsman%2C%20director%2C%20folk%20singer%20and%20other%20variations%20of%20these%20professions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20outgoing%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20most%20celebrity%20MPs%20(ten)%20belonged%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20followed%20by%20five%20MPs%20in%20the%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(AITC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Fparliament%2Fsession_track%2F2024%2Fvital_stats%2FFunctioning-17th_Lok_Sabha.pdf%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20PRS%20Legislative%20Research%2C%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20held%20a%20total%20of%20274%20sittings%2C%20which%20is%20the%20lowest%20number%20ever%20for%20a%20full%20five-year%20term.%20Only%20four%20Lok%20Sabhas%20had%20fewer%20sittings%2C%20but%20all%20of%20them%20were%20dissolved%20before%20completing%20the%20full%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20affected%20the%20number%20of%20sittings%3A%20in%202020%2C%20the%20house%20sat%20for%20only%2033%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.infogram.com%2F897ee810-7c95-48df-ac7b-64881df822d5%3Fsrc%3Dembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22699%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22List%20Of%20Celebrity%20MPs%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELow%20attendance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECelebrity%20MPs%20had%20an%20attendance%20of%2056.7%25%2C%20on%20average%2C%20our%20analysis%20of%20data%20compiled%20by%20PRS%20Legislative%20Research%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fmptrack%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20lower%20than%20the%20average%20for%20all%20MPs%20(79%25).%