ipated%20in%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20debates%20among%20the%20celebrity%20MPs%20(82)%2C%20followed%20by%20Bhojpuri%20actor-singer%20Ravi%20Kishan%20(81).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHindi%20actors%20Deol%20and%20Sinha%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20any%20debates.%20Adhikari%20participated%20in%20one%20debate%2C%20and%20Gambhir%20and%20Hans%20took%20part%20in%20three%20and%20four%20debates%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.infogram.com%2F0cabce31-f833-47d0-9af9-202a9b14d0b2%3Fsrc%3Dembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Debate%20Partcipation%20By%20Celebrity%20MPs%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22713%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFew%20questions%20asked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20MPs%20in%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20asked%20210%20questions%20each.%20Of%20the%2019%20celebrity%20MPs%2C%20only%20four%20asked%20as%20many%20or%20more%20than%20the%20national%20average%3A%20Ravi%20Kishan%20(480)%2C%20Tiwari%20(395)%2C%20Chatterjee%20(295)%20and%20Sumalatha%20Ambareesh%20(210).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinha%20did%20not%20ask%20any%20questions%3B%20Bengali%20actress-director%20Satabdi%20Roy%20Banerjee%20asked%20one%20question%3B%20folk%20singer%20Mohammad%20Sadique%20asked%20two%3B%20and%20Deol%20asked%20four%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.infogram.com%2F726e9c95-b6bc-4f4b-a2b7-8627ddf5e08b%3Fsrc%3Dembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Number%20Of%20Questions%20Asked%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%20By%20Celebrity%20MPs%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22740%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20only%20four%20celebrity%20MPs%20introduced%20private%20members%E2%80%99%20Bills%20in%20parliament%3A%20Ravi%20Kishan%20with%20ten%20Bills%2C%20followed%20by%20Anubhav%20Mohanty%20with%20three%2