r%20Komban%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20wild%20elephant%20that%20frequently%20crossed%20their%20paths.%20On%20February%203%2C%20however%2C%20Thanneer%20died%20after%20a%20re-capture%20operation%20by%20the%20Kerala%20Forest%20Department%20in%20Wayanad%E2%80%99s%20Mananthavady%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20week%20later%2C%20another%20elephant%20was%20in%20the%20news%2C%20again%20near%20Mananthavady.%20In%20the%20interactions%20that%20resulted%20between%20people%20and%20the%20Belur%20Makhna%20(%3Cem%3Emakhnas%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20tuskless%20male%20elephants)%2C%20a%20local%20died%20on%20February%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBelur%20Makhna%20killed%20a%20man%20in%20Kerala%2C%E2%80%9D%20most%20headlines%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onmanorama.com%2Fnews%2Fkerala%2F2024%2F02%2F10%2Fmassive-protest-mananthavady-radio-collared-elephant-tramples-man-death-chaligadda.html%5C%22%3Escreamed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20next%20day.%20Over%20225%20forest%20staff%20across%20both%20states%20were%20tracking%20this%20male%20for%20two%20weeks.%20Makhna%20is%20back%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20unaware%20of%20his%20fate%3A%20a%20walk%20into%20Wayanad%2C%20and%20he%20is%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.mathrubhumi.com%2Fnews%2Fkerala%2Fsharpshooter-nawab-shafat-ali-khan-also-a-part-of-mission-belur-makhana-1.9349509%5C%22%3Esharpshooter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20Karnataka%20side%20of%20the%20border%2C%20he%20could%20be%20captured%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20these%20elephants%20have%20one%20thing%20in%20common%3A%20they%20are%20both%20radio-collared%20translocated%20males%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20captured%20in%20Hassan%20and%20released%20in%20Bandipur.%20In%20the%20week%20following%20the%20incidents%2C%20the%20Kerala%20High%20Court%20called%20upon%20the%20governments%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20coordinate%20efforts%20in%20addressing%20the%20escalating%20problem%20of%20human-wildlife%20interactions%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20