EFrom%20eco-friendly%20cottages%20nestled%20amidst%20lush%20tropical%20foliage%20to%20luxurious%20beachfront%20villas%20boasting%20panoramic%20views%20of%20the%20azure%20sea%2C%20the%20resort%20caters%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20tastes%20and%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20tipping%20point%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20his%20life%20before%20he%20founded%20Barefoot%2C%20Samit%20reflects%20on%20his%20initial%20career%20aspirations.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20a%20path%20in%20finance%20and%20meticulously%20selected%20prestigious%20colleges%20to%20lead%20me%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Chennai%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342428%2Fgujarat-daman-thakore-family-drives-vintage-car-from-ahmedabad-to-london-europe-road-trip%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20relocated%20to%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%20upon%20completing%20his%20graduation%20and%20commenced%20employment%20at%20a%20renowned%20firm.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20five%20years%20of%20working%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20corporate%20finance%20didn%E2%80%99t%20resonate%20with%20me.%20It%20lacked%20the%20sense%20of%20fulfilment%20I%20sought.%20Despite%20the%20arduous%20journey%20to%20secure%20such%20a%20position%20%E2%80%94%20navigating%20academic%20challenges%2C%20seeking%20out%20the%20right%20institutions%2C%20and%20cultivating%20the%20necessary%20connections%2C%20the%20work%20became%20somewhat%20mundane.%20While%20the%20field%20suits%20many%2C%20I%20yearned%20for%20something%20more%20tangible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamit%20then%20decided%20to%20return%20to%20India.%20%E2%80%9CUpon%20my%20return%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20at%20a%20crossroads%20with%20no%20clear%20direction.%20It%20felt%20like%20starting%20anew.%20I%20opted%20to%20take%20some%20time%20off%20and%20embark%20on%20a%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquo