%20times%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2010%20years%20now%2C%20the%20eight%20rooms%20have%20been%20bustling%20with%20students%E2%80%99%20chatter%2C%20laughter%2C%20and%20cheer.%20However%2C%20the%20success%20of%20the%20model%20is%20overshadowed%20by%20the%20challenge%20of%20retention%20of%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%2C%20Seema%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20who%20live%20in%20these%20slum%20clusters%20have%20their%20roots%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremote%20villages%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20India.%20So%2C%20at%20the%20drop%20of%20a%20hat%20they%20leave%20for%20the%20village%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20because%20someone%20is%20getting%20married%2C%20other%20times%20because%20they%20are%20building%20a%20home%20there%2C%20or%20they%20need%20to%20tend%20to%20their%20fields.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20children%20miss%20months%20of%20school%20and%20then%20come%20back%20blank.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20creates%20a%20dilemma%20for%20Seema%20and%20the%20team%20of%2012%20teachers%20about%20whether%20to%20take%20the%20children%20back%20or%20not.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20them%20back%2C%20we%20will%20be%20encouraging%20them%20to%20be%20loitering%20around.%20If%20we%20take%20them%20back%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20put%20in%20an%20extra%20amount%20of%20effort%20into%20teaching%20them%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330342%2Ftamil-nadu-madhya-pradesh-policies-for-inclusive-education-improve-early-childhood-care-sonali-saini-sols-arc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esame%20concepts%3C%2Fa%3E%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Seema%20always%20chooses%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E