e%20refurbished%20or%20used%20smartphone%20market%20in%20India%20is%20projected%20to%20soar%20to%20%2410%20billion%20by%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20Avneet%20Singh%20set%20out%20to%20buy%20an%20iPhone%20for%20his%20mother%20but%20found%20the%20new%20phone%E2%80%99s%20price%20beyond%20his%20budget%20when%20he%20visited%20a%20store%20with%20his%20friend%2C%20Saket%20Saurav.%20However%2C%20an%20enterprising%20salesman%20offered%20them%20a%20second-hand%20phone%20at%20a%20significantly%20lower%20price%2C%20nearly%20Rs%2035%2C000%20less%20than%20a%20new%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20tempting%20offer%2C%20the%20phone%20lacked%20any%20checks%20and%20came%20without%20a%20warranty.%20Opting%20against%20the%20risky%20purchase%2C%20Avneet%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20together%20at%20Shopclues%2C%20he%20and%20Saket%20recognised%20a%20problem%20worth%20solving.%20Subsequently%2C%20Shopclues%20introduced%20a%20refurbished%20mobile%20category%2C%20ReNew%2C%20which%20quickly%20generated%20multi-crore%20revenue%20within%20its%20first%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20did%20extensive%20research%20on%20the%20refurbished%20mobile%20market%20and%20spotting%20an%20opportune%20time%20in%20May%202017%2C%20they%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20launched%20ReFit%20Global%20%E2%80%94%20a%20refurbished%20phone%20startup%2C%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20reduce%20e-waste%20by%20recycling%20and%20refurbishing%20second-hand%20gadgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReFit%20is%20on%20track%20to%20achieve%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%20240%20crore%20this%20financial%20year%20and%20prevent%2055%2C000%20to%2065%2C000%20phones%20from%20becoming%20e-waste%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecycling%20e-waste%2C%20promoting%20a%20circular%20economy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%